":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39e9db686d7619450bf7ae78c92cd29e82e154b","tid":519853,"uid":56203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得係人手&amp;病房病床都唔夠<br />\n病床數目十幾年加得一二百張<br />\n醫生已經加左成千個"},{"pid":"faca28d775a6e7b1cf96cd7e9d439673ab300201","tid":519853,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:19:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.bd.gov.hk/chineseT/documents/code/bfa2008/Division9.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bd.gov.hk%2FchineseT%2Fdocuments%2Fcode%2Fbfa2008%2FDivision9.pdf&d=N40w6QMbBSPJnUFZIxvBrSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=7ca6f841\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bd.gov.hk/chineseT/documents/code/bfa2008/Division9.pdf</a><br />\n該類地方的淨闊度不得少於1050毫米；<br />\n建築物每個入口的兩旁須有平坦的空間。該空間須在門的擺幅所需的範圍之外延伸不少於1200毫米，而闊度則不得少於1500毫米"},{"pid":"3f1c0fabc1d5166a01b13358c04e5bcb8225d004","tid":519853,"uid":116578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"其實要訓走廊既病人會有咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128f1559c010144c831f9396556a9c382ee4967d","tid":519853,"uid":110964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f1c0fabc1d5166a01b13358c04e5bcb8225d004","tid":519853,"uid":116578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"其實要訓走廊既病人會有咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"坐位都見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得張膠椅俾你，坐係到吊藥，有病人出院先有床俾你"},{"pid":"6a21f653279f28c129c282897a440b4abab15c4d","tid":519853,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19d89b1c0a679acd207846f5edd475bf85aa09eb","tid":519853,"uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:02:52.000Z",